        Invokes dbup migrations for updating the EdFi_Admin database accordingly.
    .EXAMPLE
        PS c:\> $parameters = @{
            PackageVersion = '2.2.1'
        }
        PS c:\> Upgrade-EdFiOdsAdminApp @parameters

